<div class="images"><a href="/wiki/Fichier:Boris_Pasternak_Signature.jpg" class="image"><img alt="Signature de Boris Pasternak" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/14/Boris_Pasternak_Signature.jpg/170px-Boris_Pasternak_Signature.jpg" decoding="async" width="170" height="37" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/14/Boris_Pasternak_Signature.jpg/255px-Boris_Pasternak_Signature.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/14/Boris_Pasternak_Signature.jpg/340px-Boris_Pasternak_Signature.jpg 2x" data-file-width="410" data-file-height="89" /></a> 
